HA-Gothick License Notice
=========================

This repository builds a composite font named "HA-Gothick" from the following upstream font resources:

1. Hack
   - Project: https://github.com/source-foundry/Hack
   - License: Modified SIL Open Font License 1.1
   - Additional notice: Bitstream Vera License
   - Reserved Font Name: "Hack" must not be used for the derived family name.

2. BIZ UDGothic
   - Project: https://github.com/googlefonts/morisawa-biz-ud-gothic
   - License: SIL Open Font License 1.1
   - Copyright holder: Morisawa Inc.

3. Nerd Fonts Symbols Only
   - Project: https://github.com/ryanoasis/nerd-fonts
   - Website: https://www.nerdfonts.com/
   - Glyph license: SIL Open Font License 1.1
   - Patcher/tooling license: MIT

Distribution intent
-------------------

The generated HA-Gothick font is intended to be distributed under the SIL Open Font License 1.1, subject to compliance with the upstream licenses above.

Key constraints
---------------

- Do not use the Reserved Font Name "Hack" in the distributed derived family name.
- Include attribution to BIZ UDGothic and Nerd Fonts glyph sources when redistributing generated binaries.
- Exclude Pomicons from the generated font because they are not covered by the intended redistribution policy in this project.

